race.comment: ADORABLE THOUGHT (10) is a So You Think filly on debut for the Lockwood/Vincent stable. Best of five trials was the latest one at Doomben when third. Three siblings to race are all multiple winners so she should have ability. MISHANI MOET (15) hasn't been far off the mark all prep. Good effort most recently over this distance in much better company. Not out of the contest. Race has been hit with scratchings and WILY JACK (7) shapes as a main beneficiary. Sound first run back from a spell and now finds an easier race. Fitter second up and rises in trip. LADY BARBAROSSA (14) has improved with each run this campaign. Should be at her peak fourth up.
